    "description": "Welcome to &quot;Night Drive,&quot; a captivating driving simulator that challenges you to navigate a seemingly endless night in search of anomalies to break a mysterious loop.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/5f0fc681a7c6e2aba92c94e423382f41.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/5f0fc681a7c6e2aba92c94e423382f41.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/5f0fc681a7c6e2aba92c94e423382f41.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In &quot;Night Drive,&quot; you find yourself behind the wheel on a deserted highway under a blanket of stars. The road ahead is long and winding, with only the faint glow of your headlights illuminating the path. The goal is simple yet profound: drive through the night until the sun rises, thereby breaking the loop and escaping the eternal darkness.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/982433a385fce244ffde424e679bf859.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/982433a385fce244ffde424e679bf859.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/982433a385fce244ffde424e679bf859.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gameplay:<br><br>Immersive Driving Experience: Feel the thrill of driving through varied landscapes under the cover of night. The realistic driving mechanics and atmospheric sound effects enhance the immersion, making every moment on the road a gripping experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/f548e7bce421e4860872ddaa29b9ff3e.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/f548e7bce421e4860872ddaa29b9ff3e.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/f548e7bce421e4860872ddaa29b9ff3e.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/c10c3893eed65a71e64303c7933f428b.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/c10c3893eed65a71e64303c7933f428b.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/c10c3893eed65a71e64303c7933f428b.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Anomalies to Discover: As you drive, keep a keen eye out for strange and unusual occurrences. These anomalies are key to breaking the loop. They could be anything from mysterious lights in the sky to cryptic road signs, or even ghostly apparitions. Each anomaly brings you one step closer to dawn.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/8e61d50eec1eaf72f074c372fcb4d0a5.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/8e61d50eec1eaf72f074c372fcb4d0a5.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/8e61d50eec1eaf72f074c372fcb4d0a5.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/f4a7f08390d3941fbc640ad1a976a9fc.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/f4a7f08390d3941fbc640ad1a976a9fc.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/f4a7f08390d3941fbc640ad1a976a9fc.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Time Loop Mechanics: Each loop presents a new opportunity to gather clues and understand the nature of your predicament. The more you drive, the more you learn about the anomalies and how to interact with them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/3ef638fd0f97f01b97bc00b8afba4770.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/3ef638fd0f97f01b97bc00b8afba4770.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/3ef638fd0f97f01b97bc00b8afba4770.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Narrative Elements: Find a way to end the endless night. Looking carefully to some sign and interactions with the anomalies, Turn left to Zebra shrine to break the curse.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/b30de900a247aaf64c5c9b8ca121b4ab.poster.avif?t=1764868541\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/b30de900a247aaf64c5c9b8ca121b4ab.webm?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059400/extras/b30de900a247aaf64c5c9b8ca121b4ab.mp4?t=1764868541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
